The paper deals with entity alignment, which is a task in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) that involves integrating knowledge from different knowledge graphs (KGs). The paper also uses a Graph Convolutional Network (GCN) based framework for learning entity and relation representations, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with cross-lingual datasets, which could fall under the category of databases (cs.DB) or information retrieval (cs.IR).
